{"tid":928726,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(法治) 網上流出37條交警收黑錢片段 與時並進用微信收錢　還有售後服務","createTime":"2018-12-05T05:16:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-05T14:29:16.000Z","uid":86509,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8b249347ced0bad988faf3e08e81c8f8145be012","tid":928726,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T05:16:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/265944843550009/posts/1960840157393794/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F265944843550009%2Fposts%2F1960840157393794%2F&d=mtzj3xCnlAAwmkpThMn1EZUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=56a7e086\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/265944843550009/posts/1960840157393794/</a><br />\n<br />\n【網上流出37條交警收黑錢片段】<br />\n【與時並進用微信收錢　還有售後服務】<br />\n<br />\n網上流傳的37條影片紀錄了今年7月到11月期間，交警於河南安陽一個高速公路超載檢查站收黑錢的片段。<br />\n<br />\n除了收現金和香煙，還接受微信支付，每次收$200，相熟就收$100。而且提供售後服務，就算不是當值時間，只要在微信收到錢，可以即時轉達當值同事，放司機一馬。<br />\n<br />\n警員會叫司機遮擋車牌逆行通過監測站，或者幫他調換駕駛證，不過收費就貴許多了。有貨車司機不想被扣分，換個駕駛證處理，當值的民警不願意，就找相熟的輔警。「我有他的電話，平常也有過聯繫，他說那個沒問題，我給當值民警說一聲就行了。他就說平時給別人管事，都是2000塊錢，我們不是第一次打交道了，我給你便宜點就行了，以後還一直共事，最後要了1000塊錢。」<br />\n<br />\n影片曝光後，安陽交警治超大隊長曾接受訪問指，隊內只有3名正式警員帶領24個輔警執法。涉嫌收黑錢的都是輔警，他們趁民警晚上休息期間，單獨違規執法。<br />\n<br />\n不過安陽交警於周一公布，治超大隊長和隊內3名民警均被停職，亦已開除10名證實收黑錢的輔警，其餘14名輔警則暫時停職接受調查。<br />\n<br />\n#超載違規<br />\n#收黑錢<br />\n#有線中國組"},{"pid":"9b4fcde568aedddff8aa0cba83056ab65305bf8f","tid":928726,"uid":86509,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T05:31:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://blog.menclub.hk/muddwater3000/wp-content/uploads/sites/175/2018/02/Screen-Shot-2018-02-20-at-8.41.16-PM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.menclub.hk%2Fmuddwater3000%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F175%2F2018%2F02%2FScreen-Shot-2018-02-20-at-8.41.16-PM.png&h=24e4630a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ba52602ccab6adfb5605bee37f04ee4c8de9db6a","tid":928726,"uid":90704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T05:42:03.000Z","msg":"Xianggong 公安收唔收we7?"},{"pid":"58e2945ea8d2b8d1254f34b223c1ca0880df85c5","tid":928726,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T05:48:44.000Z","msg":"支那不驚喜"},{"pid":"bca8f3e1e2da56fa69f304a47baec9bd3b87b6a1","tid":928726,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba52602ccab6adfb5605bee37f04ee4c8de9db6a","tid":928726,"uid":90704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T05:42:03.000Z","msg":"Xianggong 公安收唔收we7?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T05:50:24.000Z","msg":"XGGA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e4580bbbc7e88b901e3e45e6ea7f2116566e683","tid":928726,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T07:16:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f2d8360173423a2d4af51c7c4d28bcb009079c2","tid":928726,"uid":171058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T08:13:18.000Z","msg":"依咁L樣既法冶國"},{"pid":"aa3171ebe044a5fd5d633426a6753fb1f0e9f33e","tid":928726,"uid":33668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T08:14:54.000Z","msg":"所以話香港收費系統真係好落後"},{"pid":"dfb20102fa4c59bb13c75e85a0a45c9d422a2b01","tid":928726,"uid":2566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T08:16:40.000Z","msg":"用微信收黑錢會唔會鳩岸左D"},{"pid":"d6bf73f9e4540b2ec6f7e1b2c299bf1429dbccd5","tid":928726,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T10:50:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6830ffafe0722338d1b5171c9eac2ddba3261143","tid":928726,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T14:29:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}